text: Ate yakuba ne akhi'a ki he mere putaro! Tusim sare ika him daravaze vicom pravesa na karana sagom vakha-vakha daravazi'am tom adara jana. Ate maim tuhanu alaha di kise gala tom nahim baca sakada hukama tam basa alaha da hi hai. Maim use upara bharosa karada ham ate bharosa karana vali'am nu usa upara hi bharosa karana cahida hai
